{"word":"H2370 - חֲזָא - chăzâʼ - khaz-aw' - Behold","slug":"H2370","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חֲזָא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>chăzâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khaz-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Behold"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05D6;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D7;&#x05D6;&#x05D0; - cha&#x0306;za&#x0302;'  cha&#x0306;za&#x0302;h</b> - <i>khaz-aw', khaz-aw'</i><p/>(Chaldee); corresponding to <a href=\"#/H2372\">H2372</a>; to <i>gaze</i> upon; mentally to <i>dream</i>, <i>be usual</i> (that is, <i>seem</i>): - behold, have [a dream], see, be wont."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2376\">H2376</a>, <a href=\"#/H2379\">H2379</a>"}]}